. preserve

. keep if inlist(year, 2010, 2011, 2012, 2013)
(9,062 observations deleted)

. collapse (mean) log_raw_qty log_raw_spend (firstnm) spend_2013 treated, by(ca
> tegory year)

. reshape wide log_raw_qty log_raw_spend, i(category treated) j(year)
(j = 2010 2011 2012 2013)

Data                               Long   ->   Wide
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Number of observations              240   ->   60          
Number of variables                   6   ->   11          
j variable (4 values)              year   ->   (dropped)
xij variables:
                            log_raw_qty   ->   log_raw_qty2010 log_raw_qty2011 
> ... log_raw_qty2013
                          log_raw_spend   ->   log_raw_spend2010 log_raw_spend2
> 011 ... log_raw_spend2013
